Global Phosphate-Fixing Biofertilizers Market Insights
Phosphate-Fixing Biofertilizers Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 2.5 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 9.7% from 2024 to 2030.

Phosphate-Fixing Biofertilizers Market Overview
The global phosphate-fixing biofertilizers market is experiencing significant growth due to the increasing demand for sustainable agricultural practices. The market size was valued at approximately USD 2.5 billion in 2024 and is projected to grow at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2025 to 2030. This growth is driven by the need to reduce dependency on chemical fertilizers, boost soil health, and promote eco-friendly farming practices. Phosphate-fixing biofertilizers, which aid in enhancing soil fertility and improving plant growth by making phosphorous more available to crops, have gained popularity in various regions globally. The increasing awareness of environmental concerns, coupled with the expansion of organic farming, is expected to fuel further market growth.

